refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;

 stringDomDocumentType::public_id




 This function returns the public id of the document type.

&reftitle.returnvalues;


 Returns the public id of the DomDocumentType, as a
 string.

  &reftitle.examples;


   The following example echos nothing.

    Retrieving the public id


<?php
include("example.inc");

if (!$dom = domxml_open_mem($xmlstr)) {
  echo "Error while parsing the document\n";
  exit;
}

$doctype = $dom->doctype();
echo $doctype->public_id();
?>
